ComicInfo.Summary: "Superviolence." It's a title that says it all, and then some! In a secret BIOWAR facility somewhere in Texas, a security breach has occurred. Under cover of night, a single agent has been sent to kill all personnel and release floating terror into the skies. In response, Miranda Zero sends in her own lone agent. Now two men are locked in deady hand-to-hand battle, enduring unimaginable pain!
